org.drip.calc.output
Class ComponentOutput

java.lang.Object
  org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      org.drip.calc.output.ComponentOutput

public class ComponentOutput
extends Serializer

This class serves as a place holder for analytical single component output measures, optionally across scenarios. Contains measure maps for unadjusted base IR/credit curves, flat delta/gamma bump measure maps for IR/credit bump curves, tenor bump double maps for IR/credit curves, flat/recovery bumped measure maps for recovery bumped credit curves
